## Case 1: Complex User Schema
+ (
    !^$id**,
    !^$username*,
    ?^$email,
    ^&is_admin: false,
    !@Timestamp created_at***
);

## Case 2: Nested Data (Product Item)
+ product: (
    $sku**,
    @USD price: 19.99,
    [
        ( $name: "Red", $stock: 100 ) |
        ( $name: "Blue", $stock: 50 )
    ] variants
);

## Case 3: Mixed visibility/exposure (The "Shadow" batch)
+ (
    !^!exposed_val: 1,
    !^hidden_val: 2,
    !internal_val: 3
);
